Sentencas: LSGM8282 (La0.8Sr0.2Ga0.8Mg0.2O3-delta) material as the solid electrolyte for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells was synthesized by solid-state reaction.
Titulo: Fabrication characteristics of SOFC single cell with thin LSGM electrolyte via tape-casting and co-sintering

Sentencas: LSGM material with single phase was obtained by optimizing calcination and sintering temperatures.
Titulo: Fabrication characteristics of SOFC single cell with thin LSGM electrolyte via tape-casting and co-sintering

Sentencas: LSGM electrolyte layer, buffer layer (LDC) and anode layers (NiO/GDC) and its assembly were fabricated by the tape-casting and co-sintering process.
Titulo: Fabrication characteristics of SOFC single cell with thin LSGM electrolyte via tape-casting and co-sintering

Sentencas: Power density, impedance and durability of SOFC single cell were evaluated at intermediate temperatures.
Titulo: Fabrication characteristics of SOFC single cell with thin LSGM electrolyte via tape-casting and co-sintering

Sentencas: As the result, LSGM showed high ionic conductivity of 0.16 S cm(-1) at 800 degrees C
Titulo: Fabrication characteristics of SOFC single cell with thin LSGM electrolyte via tape-casting and co-sintering

Sentencas: The single cell showed good power density of 1.24 W cm(-2) at 2 A cm(-2), ohmic resistance of 0.07 Omega cm(2) at 800 degrees C and durability of 500 h. (C) 2016
Titulo: Fabrication characteristics of SOFC single cell with thin LSGM electrolyte via tape-casting and co-sintering
